<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Your Temporary Password</h1>

    <p>Hello,</p>

    <p>As requested, we have reset your password. Your temporary password is:</p>

    <p style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 4px;">
      <%= @temp_password %>
    </p>

    <p>You can use this password to login to your account. After logging in, you can change your password using the 'Change Password' button if you wish.</p>

    <p>If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
  </body>
</html>